 Berlin.  Prints of similar biblical subjects, size, quality of impression, condition and subject matter range from $1401-$2424. The subject property is most comparable in quality of impression to prints at the high end of this range. A search of etchings by the artist in galleries in the United States only turned up a single venue, Spaightwood Galleries in Upton, Massachusetts where a number etchings are available for between $1750-$4500. Most of the etchings available for sale are considerably smaller than the subject property. The etching most closely approximating the subject property in size and quality of impression is available for $4,500 and is the basis for estimating the subject property's replacement value\n"),(ItemDescription,"A biblical scene of the flood."),(ItemCost,""),(ItemFax,""),(ItemTel,""),(ItemCity,""),(ItemAddress,""),(ItemExhibitionsAndPublications,""),(ItemProvenance,""),(ItemCondition,"Good: Some stains and creases. Good impression."),(ItemMediumMaterialsTechniques,"Etching"),(ItemVerso,""),(ItemRecto,""),(ItemPhotographNumbers,""),(ItemSignatureInscriptionsMarkings,"Signed in the plate lower left, Battista Franco Inu"),(ItemItemDepth,""),(ItemItemWidth,""),(ItemItemHeight,""),(ItemItemMeasurement,"Sheet: 10 1/2\" x 17\" (27 cm x 43 cm)"),(ItemFrameDepth,""),(ItemFrameWidth,""),(ItemFrameHeight,""),(ItemFrameMeasurement,"25 1/4\" x 30 1/4\""),(ItemSupportBaseFrame,"Glazed silver gilt wood frame"),(ItemSubjectOrTitle,"The Deluge, Le deluge universel, 3, Bartsch"),(ItemCountryOrNationality,"Italy"),(ItemArtistDate,"1498-1561"),(ItemArtistOrMaker,"Giovanni Battista Franco Inu"),(ItemItemDate,""),(ItemDateOrPeriod,"16th century"),(ItemTypeOfObject,"Print"),(ItemLocation,""),(ItemInspectionDate,""),(ItemProjectNumber,""),(ItemClient,""),(ItemInspector,""),(ItemDataSheetNumber,"17, Hanson #66")], images = [Pic {picSize = ImageSize {dim = TheHeight, size = 3.0, units = Inches}, picCrop = ImageCrop {topCrop = 0, bottomCrop = 0, leftCrop = 0, rightC